20
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:14,228
It's called this-that, the this-that law, in the Pali.

21
00:03:15,669 --> 00:03:16,950
And it goes something like this.

22
00:03:17,891 --> 00:03:20,415
Because that happened in the past, this happens now.

23
00:03:21,036 --> 00:03:23,800
And because that didn't happen, this doesn't happen.

24
00:03:24,455 --> 00:03:25,475
of this does happen.

25
00:03:25,817 --> 00:03:27,519
It depends how you want to interpret it.

26
00:03:27,538 --> 00:03:32,625
So that's basically the way most people would think of karma in the sense of cause and effect.

27
00:03:33,325 --> 00:03:37,229
